<template>
  <PDFView msg="Welcome to Your Vue.js App" />
  <RefView> </RefView>
</template>

<script>
import PDFView from './components/PDFView.vue'
import RefView from './components/RefView.vue'

import axios from 'axios';

export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    PDFView,
    RefView
  }
}


axios.get('http://localhost:8888/api/data')
  .then(response => {
    this.data = response.data.data; // 获取数据
  })
  .catch(error => {
    console.error('There was an error!', error);
  });


</script>

<style>
#app {
  font-family: Avenir, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-align: center;
  color: #2c3e50;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  position: absolute;
}
</style>
